headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Lampadati Michelli GT & Rune Cheburek
content: Not one but two classics hit the streets of Los Santos this week. The Lampadati Michelli is a sports racer straight out of the golden age of deregulation, and if the Rune Cheburek doesn’t scratch that itch you’ve had ever since the Cold War ended, nothing will. That’s right: the good old days are here to stay.
